gw.api.system

Class PCLoggingMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.system.PCLoggingMarker

  • public final class PCLoggingMarker
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class for defining logging markers which are used in PC. The approach of explicit declaration of those markers was chosen based on following reasons: - The relation between profiler tag and marker is not necessarily one-to-one, possibly there could be one marker associated with few profiler tags - Profiler-based approach for intentional logging is not the only one (two others we'll probably use are: manual logging instructions, instrumenting generic code with logging e.g. work queues) - Defining logging markers explicitly in XXLoggingMarker class was initially introduced in PL code so we're trying to be consistent across all the apps
